name: I can can I I everything else
description: An "ad" using AI generated language from Joel Simon's "Dimension of Dialogue" series (where two neural nets learn to communicate through their own emergent visual language) appears to be targeted to a monster type who would ordinarily be assailing Saint Anthony the Hermit were he not so distracted by what we humans might assume to be the latest model of a jellyfish typewriter. Not available in all states.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
